I"/ž<p>I moved from the Pelican Python static website generator. This is a step by step tutorial to build a <strong>static website with Jekyll and Github Pages</strong>.</p>

<p>Sources:</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://jekyllrb.com/">Jekyllâ€™s blog</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://help.github.com/en/github/working-with-github-pages/creating-a-github-pages-site-with-jekyll">Create a Github pages site with Jekyll</a></li>
